    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''To Speak With One's Own Voice'' (Op-Ed, Aug. 8):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''To Speak With One's Own Voice'' (Op-Ed, Aug. 8):</p>
        <p>Samuel G. Freedman writes of Senator Joseph I. Lieberman's Modern Orthodox Judaism, which believes in ''the value of engaging with the larger society.''</p>
        <p>Indeed, the article is a powerful rallying call not only to American Jews but also to all Americans to stand up and be counted in this election to vote to continue us on the path of progress rather than turning back to the xenophobic years of the past.</p>
        <p>LEON BANK  Tucson, Aug. 8, 2000</p>
      </block>
